nicipality\n| area_blank2_km2   = 274.6\n| population_as_of  = 2013 census\n| population_blank1_title = Town\n| population_blank1 = 2401\n| population_density_blank1_km2 = auto\n| population_blank2_title = Municipality\n| population_blank2 = 4895\n| population_density_blank2_km2 = auto\n| coordinates = {{coord|43|33|N|19|04|E|region:BA|display=inline, title}}\n| area_code = 58\n| website = \n| footnotes = \n| timezone=[[Central European Time|CET]]\n| utc_offset=+1\n| timezone_DST = [[Central European Summer Time|CEST]]\n| utc_offset_DST = +2\n| unit_pref= Metric\n}}\n\n'''\u010cajni\u010de''' ({{lang-sr-cyr|\u0427\u0430\u0458\u043d\u0438\u0447\u0435}}; {{IPA-sh|t\u0283\u00e2\u02d0jni\u02d0t\u0283\u025b|pron}}) is a town and municipality located in [[Republika Srpska]], an entity of [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]]. As of 2013, the town has a population of 2,401 inhabitants, while the municipality has 4,895 inhabitants.\n\n==Settlements==\nAside from the town of \u010cajni\u010de, the municipality includes the following settlements:\n{{div col|colwidth=22em}}\n* [[Avlija]]\n* [[Batkovi\u0107i (\u010cajni\u010de)|Batkovi\u0107i]]\n* [[Batoti\u0107i]]\n* [[Batovo (\u010cajni\u010de)|Batovo]]\n* [[Bezujno]]\n* [[Borajno]]\n* [[Brezovice (\u010cajni\u010de)|Brezovice]]\n* [[Bu\u010dkovi\u0107i na Bezujanci]]\n* [[\u0110akovi\u0107i (\u010cajni\u010de)|\u0110akovi\u0107i]]\n* [[Glamo\u010devi\u0107i]]\n* [[Glo\u017ein]]\n* [[Hunkovi\u0107i]]\n* [[Ifsar]]\n* [[Kamen (\u010cajni\u010de)|Kamen]]\n* [[Kapov Han]]\n* [[Karovi\u0107i (\u010cajni\u010de)|Karovi\u0107i]]\n* [[Krstac (\u010cajni\u010de)|Krstac]]\n* [[La\u0111evci (\u010cajni\u010de)|La\u0111evci]]\n* [[Luke (\u010cajni\u010de)|Luke]]\n* [[Me\u0111urje\u010dje]]\n* [[Metaljka (\u010cajni\u010de)|Metaljka]]\n* [[Milatkovi\u0107i]]\n* [[Miljeno]]\n* [[Mi\u0161tar]]\n* [[Podavrelo]]\n* [[Ponikve (\u010cajni\u010de)|Ponikve]]\n* [[Prvanj]]\n* [[Slatina (\u010cajni\u010de)|Slatina]]\n* [[Staroni\u0107i]]\n* [[Stopi\u0107i]]\n* [[Sudi\u0107i (\u010cajni\u010de)|Sudi\u0107i]]\n* [[Todorovi\u0107i (\u010cajni\u010de)|Todorovi\u0107i]]\n* [[Trpinje]]\n* [[Tubrojevi\u0107i]]\n* [[Zaborak]]\n{{div col end}}\n\n==Demographics==\n{{Historical populations\n| type = \n| percentages = pagr\n|1971|11602 |1991|8956 |2013|4895\n}}\nAccording to the 2013 census results, the municipality of \u010cajni\u010de has 4,895 inhabitants.\n\n===Ethnic groups===\nThe ethnic composition of the municipality:\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Ethnic group\n! Population<br>1971\n! Population<br>1991<ref name=\"popis2013\">{{cite web |title=Popis 2013 u BiH \u2013 \u010cajni\u010de |url=http://www.statistika.ba/?show=12&id=20630 |website=statistika.ba |accessdate=29 December 2018 |language=Bosnian}}</ref>\n! Population<br>2013<ref name=\"popis2013\" />\n|-\n|[[Serbs of Bosnia and Herzegovina|Serbs]]\n|align=\"right\"|5,353\n|align=\"right\"|4,709\n|align=\"right\"|3,972\n|-\n|[[Bosniaks]]/[[Muslims (nationality)|Muslims]]\n|align=\"right\"|6,065\n|align=\"right\"|4,024\n|align=\"right\"|884\n|-\n|[[Croats of Bosnia and Herzegovina|Croats]]\n|align=\"right\"|29\n|align=\"right\"|5\n|align=\"right\"|6\n|-\n|Others\n|align=\"right\"|155\n|align=\"right\"|218\n|align=\"right\"|33\n|- class=\"sortbottom\"\n|'''Total'''\n|align=\"right\"|11,602\n|align=\"right\"|8,956\n|align=\"right\"|4,895\n|}\n\n==Notable people==\n* [[Hanka Paldum]], Bosnian singer\n\n==See also==\n*[[Municipalities of Republika Srpska]]\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n* Official results from the book ''Ethnic composition of Bosnia-Herzegovina population, by municipalities and settlements, 1991''. census, Zavod za statistiku Bosne i Hercegovine - Bilten no.234, Sarajevo 1991.\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category|\u010cajni\u010de}}\n\n{{Political divisions of Bosnia and Herzegovina}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Cajnice}}\n[[Category:Populated places in \u010cajni\u010de]]\n[[Category:\u010cajni\u010de| ]]\n\n{{\u010cajni\u010de-geo-stub}}\n", "name_us