/08/skops-kommunala-valjarbarometer-20-augusti-2019/|title=SKOP:s kommunala v\u00e4ljarbarometer, 20 augusti 2019|website=SKOP|language=sv|access-date=2019-08-20}}</ref>\n|25 Jun\u201316 Jul 2019\n|1,048\n|7.5\n|style=\"background:#F9BDC5;\"| '''27.4'''\n|5.6\n|10.8\n|5.8\n|22.8\n|6.0\n|11.7\n|2.5\n|style=\"background:{{Swedish Social Democratic Party/meta/color}};color:#FFFFFF;\"| 4.6\n|-\n|SKOP<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://skop.se/politik/2019/04/kommunal-valjarbarometer-24-april-2019/|title=Kommunal v\u00e4ljarbarometer, 24 april 2019|website=SKOP|language=sv|access-date=2019-04-24}}</ref>\n|7-27 Mar 2019\n|1,510\n|7.3\n|style=\"background:#F9BDC5;\"| '''29.5'''\n|4.2\n|10.7\n|6.1\n|21.4\n|6.1\n|10.9\n|3.8\n|style=\"background:{{Swedish Social Democratic Party/meta/color}};color:#FFFFFF;\"| 8.1\n|- style=\"background:#E9E9E9;\"\n| [[2018 Swedish local elections|2018 municipal election]]\n| data-sort-value=\"2018-09-09\"| 9 Sep 2018\n| \u2013\n| 7.7\n| style=\"background:#F9BDC5;\"| '''27.6'''\n| 4.6\n| 9.7\n| 6.8\n| 20.1\n| 5.2\n| 12.7\n| 5.6\n| style=\"background:{{Swedish Social Democratic Party/meta/color}};color:#FFFFFF;\"| 7.5\n|}\n\n== See also ==\n*[[Opinion polling for the 2018 Swedish general election]]\n*[[Opinion polling for the 2014 Swedish general election]]\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n== External links ==\n*[http://pollofpolls.se/ List of polls on pollofpolls.se] {{in lang|sv}}\n*[https://val.digital/ List of polls and aggregation on val.digital] {{in lang|sv}}\n\n*[https://www.kantarsifo.se/ Sifo] {{in lang|sv}}\n*[https://novus.se/ Novus] {{in lang|sv}}\n*[https://www.ipsos.com/sv-se/ Ipsos] {{in lang|sv}}\n*[https://skop.se/ SKOP] {{in lang|sv}}\n*[https://scb.se/ SCB] {{in lang|sv}}\n*[https://demoskop.se/ Demoskop] {{in lang|sv}}\n*[https://inizio.se/ Inizio] {{in lang|sv}}\n*[http://sentio.no/sv/ Sentio] {{in lang|sv}}\n\n\n\n[[Category:Opinion polling in Sweden]]\n[[Category:Opinion polling for future elections|Sweden]]\n", "text_old": 